data.description: This ranch home offers the perfect blend of indoor and outdoor living, making it an ideal haven for those who value space, comfort, and tranquility. Enjoy the spacious back deck, a fenced yard for privacy, and an oversized 2-car garage. The primary bedroom has an en suite bathroom, and there's an additional full bathroom off the main hallway. The finished basement offers extra living space. There are two living room areas off the kitchen, one in the front of the house (with a big bay window) and one in the back of the house (with double doors that open to the back deck). The home is in Canal Winchester School District. Agents see A2A.
